ce = CategoricalEncoder(max_unique_ratio=0.5)
X = pd.DataFrame({'completely_unique': ['a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e'],
    'too_unique': ['a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'a'], 'not_unique': ['a', 'b', 'a',
    'a', 'a'], 'not_feature': [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]})
features = ce._detect_features(X)
assert features == ['not_unique']
